    my good publican!           

03:27.700 --> 03:29.800
I'm of a Dickensian spirit      
             today.             

03:29.900 --> 03:32.300
I've just come from             
the Antiquarian Book Fair,      

03:32.400 --> 03:34.600
where I managed to luck         
