first edition of Charles        
Dickens' <i>Tale of Two Cities.</i>    

03:37.700 --> 03:39.200
                            Wow!

03:39.200 --> 03:40.300
            If you don't mind   
                      my asking,

03:40.400 --> 03:42.300
         how much does something
      like this cost, Dr. Crane?

03:42.400 --> 03:44.200
Well, uh, Woody, money          
isn't really the issue,         

03:44.300 --> 03:47.100
but, uh, around $1,200.         

03:47.100 --> 03:48.400
              (scoffs, snickers)

