11:55.600 --> 11:57.000
            Listen,             

11:57.100 --> 11:58.600
      will you tell Woody       
      that I left his car       

11:58.700 --> 12:01.100
  outside the United terminal.  

12:01.200 --> 12:03.200
          Or American.          

12:03.200 --> 12:04.900
    It doesn't really           
      make any difference.      

12:05.000 --> 12:08.300
    They all tow them           
to the same place anyway.       

12:09.800 --> 12:10.900
         Sam, is that Miss Howe?

12:10.900 --> 12:12.400
                  Ask her if she
                  has my wallet.

12:12.500 --> 12:14.700
                    I need my   
            driver's license.   

12:14.700 --> 12:17.600
Actually, you don't             
have to worry about             
that right now, Wood.           

12:17.600 --> 12:19.600
What are you doing?             
Where are you going?            

12:19.700 --> 12:21.900
    I'm-I'm going home          
    to San Diego, Sam.          

12:22.000 --> 12:23.700
I want to try and forget Boston.

12:23.800 --> 12:27.100
        I want to erase         
the last three years of my life.

12:27.200 --> 12:28.400
    It's been five, Rebecca.    

12:28.400 --> 12:30.600
     Has it been that long?     

12:32.800 --> 12:34.100
              Hey, Sam, does she
                 have my wallet?

12:34.200 --> 12:36.000
You still have Woody's          
wallet, don't you?              

12:36.100 --> 12:38.500
  Yeah, sure, how do you think  
I'm paying for this call?       

12:38.500 --> 12:41.500
     Hell, how do you think     
  I'm paying for this flight?   

12:41.500 --> 12:44.700
Yeah, she still has it.         

12:49.200 --> 12:51.300
Honey, listen to me.            

12:51.300 --> 12:53.400
You can't run away from         
your problems like this.        

12:53.500 --> 12:55.000
        Sam, Sam, look,         
    the only reason I called    

12:55.100 --> 12:57.900
      was to say good-bye       
 and thank you for everything.  

12:58.000 --> 13:00.700
 It's really meant a lot to me. 
            Bye-bye.            

13:01.700 --> 13:03.600
Oh, miss, did you remember      
your credit card?               

